      {
        "role": "COMPANION",
        "content": "Great job, Tom! That was a very polite response. When being shown to your table, you can also say something simple like, \"Thank you,\" or \"Thanks, I'm looking forward to my meal.\" Would you like to try saying something as you follow the host to your table? If you’re not sure, I can give you a hint!"
      },
